Templates.name: sap.fe.core.controllerextensions.ViewState.applyNavigationParameters
Templates.helpDescription:
Apply navigation parameters - is called only if navigation type is not iAppState.

This function is meant to be individually overridden by consuming controllers, but not to be called directly. The override execution is: {@link sap.ui.core.mvc.OverrideExecution.After}.

Templates.name: sap.fe.core.controllerextensions.ViewState.applyViewState
Templates.helpDescription: Applies the given view state to this extensions view.
